{{Infobox language |name = Etkywan |altname=Icen |nativename= |states = [[Nigeria]] |region = [[Taraba State|Taraba]] |speakers = {{sigfig|50200|2}} |date=2000 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Benue–Congo languages|Benue–Congo]] |fam4= [[Jukunoid languages|Jukunoid]] |fam5= Central |fam6= Kpan–Icen |iso3=ich |glotto=etky1238 |glottorefname=Etkywan }}
'''Etkywan''' (Etekwe), or '''Icen''' (Itchen), also known as ''Kentu'' or ''Nyidu'', is a [[Jukunoid language]] of [[Nigeria]].
