==Morphology==

===Nouns===

====Pluralization====
Pluralization is marked on nouns with the suffix {{IPA|/-lAr/}}, which has the two forms {{IPA|/-lar/}} and {{IPA|/-lær/}}, depending on [[vowel harmony]]. Plular {{IPA|/ɑ/}} never rounding even follow {{IPA|/u/}} or {{IPA|/i/}} for.

